WEBVTT

00:01.022 --> 00:02.304
Narrator: <i>Christmas...</i>

00:02.362 --> 00:05.136
<i>The time of year when
the chill in the air...</i>

00:05.256 --> 00:07.601
<i>brings out the warmth in your heart.</i>

00:08.013 --> 00:10.099
<i>But what happens when
Christmas spirit...</i>

00:10.141 --> 00:12.807
<i>meets 140 degrees outside?</i>

00:18.719 --> 00:21.263
Lola: Bugs, Christmas is almost here.
Are you excited?

00:21.383 --> 00:25.992
Bugs: Not really. It's December
and it's 100 degrees out here.

00:26.072 --> 00:29.146
Lola: What are you saying?
Bugs: It's too hot for Christmas.

00:29.192 --> 00:30.833
Lola: Too hot for Christmas?

00:30.882 --> 00:32.913
How can you say such a thing?

00:32.946 --> 00:35.159
I feel woozy. Oh! Like I'm gonna faint.

00:35.382 --> 00:38.071
Bugs: That's because
you're wearing a parka.

00:38.105 --> 00:40.573
Lola: Huh? Oh.

00:44.875 --> 00:46.774
Oh, yeah.
That's much better.

00:46.813 --> 00:48.350
What were we talking about again?

00:48.391 --> 00:50.301
Bugs: Not doing Christmas this year.

00:50.356 --> 00:52.058
Ohh!

00:54.033 --> 00:58.997
